    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful luster, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains very solid and drives smoothly, making it a reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
